-- Adidas Forecasts Higher Revenue, Earnings as `Momentum' Continues in 2011
-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 2010-11-04T06:41:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-04/adidas-forecasts-higher-revenue-earnings-as-momentum-continues-in-2011.html
Adidas AG expects sales and net
income to increase next year as “momentum” continues from
2010.  The German sports-gear maker forecast currency-neutral
group sales to rise at a mid-single-digit percentage rate and
expects earnings per share to outpace revenue growth. It sees
EPS growing 10 percent to 15 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  